name: sfchronicle
text: JUST IN: President Trump completed a second dose of Remdesivir “without complication” on Saturday and has “made substantial progress since diagnosis,” according to a memo from Sean Conley, the president's physician. https://t.co/j7yntf1Gk6

name: sfchronicle
text:
